    "name": "农场商店模拟器演示",
    "steam_appid": 3272580,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/a02db74b02273195225b0fdca5b3be2f.poster.avif?t=1737478258\" width=605 height=49 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/a02db74b02273195225b0fdca5b3be2f.webm?t=1737478258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >想象一下继承了一个农场和一家店铺。你会怎么做？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是的，这里一团糟。是的，需要工作。但它是你的—而且是免费的。在这个经济环境下？！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/d9f0b22354adc34adf141165888a069e.poster.avif?t=1737478258\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/d9f0b22354adc34adf141165888a069e.webm?t=1737478258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/d9f0b22354adc34adf141165888a069e.mp4?t=1737478258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>恢复你的农场</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将这片荒废的土地变成繁荣的农场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >种植自己的作物，照顾动物（即将推出），并升级周围环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这将需要努力，但不久你就能获得新工具，改善建筑，并定制你梦想中的农场。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/4f4d59bf9771c7bf1cd37fdc2cc03b3d.poster.avif?t=1737478258\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/4f4d59bf9771c7bf1cd37fdc2cc03b3d.webm?t=1737478258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/4f4d59bf9771c7bf1cd37fdc2cc03b3d.mp4?t=1737478258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>开设你自己的店铺</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为什么要把你的作物和产品卖给别人呢？你可以自己来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >听说过农贸市场吗？这家店已经解决了“农民”的部分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整理你的店铺，管理货架上的商品，并处理所有财务！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直接销售给顾客，或者雇佣帮助—毕竟，你只是个人类。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/29b15700f47a2bdfd5e0ff3c7071eb6e.poster.avif?t=1737478258\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/29b15700f47a2bdfd5e0ff3c7071eb6e.webm?t=1737478258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/29b15700f47a2bdfd5e0ff3c7071eb6e.mp4?t=1737478258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>掌握多任务处理的艺术</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时经营农场和店铺并不容易。但你能做到！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在照顾作物、服务顾客和管理混乱之间平衡时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自己动手，或雇佣帮手，并订购你尚未生产的商品（至少目前还没有）。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会专注于严格的商业模式吗？还是追求个性化和可持续性？或许两者兼顾？决定权在你手中。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/fc08a9e9534768ae1e640f75c7692d2e.poster.avif?t=1737478258\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/fc08a9e9534768ae1e640f75c7692d2e.webm?t=1737478258\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3272580/extras/fc08a9e9534768ae1e640f75c7692d2e.mp4?t=1737478258\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
